 **Work placement**  
In no particular order:

- enthusiasm;
- initiative; and
- patience.

**Junior designer** \*  
All of the above traits, as well as being:

- fastidious;
- punctual;
- articulate;
- thick-skinned;
- intelligent; and, of course
- creative.

\*A good knowledge of the usual industry programmes is a fundamental requirement.
